### GET AUTH
# @name login
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/auth
Accept: application/json
###
@Token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### GET ALL
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json
### Invoice
POST {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "CustomerId": 1,
  "CurrencyId": 1,
  "CreatedBy": "ingenierfonseca",
  "Items": [
    {
      "Description": "Extracción Molar",
      "Quantity": 2,
      "UnitPrice": 600,
      "Discount": 0,
