### Invoice
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice/1
Accept: application/json

### Invoice Dashboard
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice/dashboard?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5&search=
Accept: application/json

### Invoice Dashboard
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice/dashboard-customers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5&search=
Accept: application/json

### Invoice Customer
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice/customer/2
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json

### Invoice Customer Pyments
GET {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice/customer/2/payments
Accept: application/json


### PUT Invoice
PUT {{MedicalSuiteNova_HostAddress}}/api/invoice/1
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

